exceptions.exn: In environment X, X', Y, Y' : Type RX : relation2 X X' R : relation2 X Y RY : relation2 Y Y' R' : relation2 X' Y' H : diagram RX R RY R' The term "R'" has type "X' -> Y' -> Prop" while it is expected to have type "X -> X' -> Prop" (cannot unify "X" and "X'").

exceptions.tactic: apply incl_trans with (R := R) (S := RY) (T := RX).
